        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Activation:</strong> <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Always Active\" aria-label=\"Always Active\">8</span></p><p><em>You’ve learned when to withdraw and when to commit to a position, holding it unflinchingly.</em></p><p>The @UUID[Compendium.cosmere-rpg.actions.Item.I1CQjZicYdeG9NCN]{Brace} action adds two disadvantages to attacks against you, instead of one.</p><p>Additionally, while you’re using a shield to Brace, allies within 5 feet of you can Brace as if they had cover or a shield.</p>",
            "chat": "<p><strong>Activation:</strong> <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Always Active\" aria-label=\"Always Active\">8</span></p><p>The @UUID[Compendium.cosmere-rpg.actions.Item.I1CQjZicYdeG9NCN]{Brace} action adds two disadvantages to attacks against you, instead of one, and allies can Brace behind your shield.</p>",
            "short": "<p><strong>Activation:</strong> <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Always Active\" aria-label=\"Always Active\">8</span></p><p>The @UUID[Compendium.cosmere-rpg.actions.Item.I1CQjZicYdeG9NCN]{Brace} action adds two disadvantages to attacks against you, instead of one.</p><p>Additionally, while you’re using a shield to Brace, allies within 5 feet of you can Brace as if they had cover or a shield.</p>"
